Invocation Name: sleep assistant
des: This skill is designed to help you fall asleep at night by providing you with a short visualization and breathing exercise and some calming sounds to get your mind ready for a good night sleep. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
